data.description: Single floor living at it's finest! Beautiful Ranch home in the City of Plattsburgh. 3-4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and attached 2 car garage. Open concept living room, dining room & kitchen. Deck off of kitchen overlooks backyard with new privacy fence! Spacious primary suite with ensuite bath & walk-in closet. 2nd Bedroom on 1st floor as well as Bonus 3rd bedroom above the garage. Previous 4th bedroom is now an updated laundry room, but could be turned back into a 4th bedroom if needed. This house is ready for you to move in! Call for a tour today!
